content: I do not have personal preferences but speaking in general, some popular late-night snacks are chips, popcorn, chocolate, cookies, nuts, and fruits like bananas or apples. you might also want to try some salty or savory snacks such as instant noodles or microwavable popcorn. additionally, some convenient stores may offer sandwiches, pizza, hot dogs, or other ready-to-eat snacks for a quick bite.
